page.content: {KINGMOOR CONTRIBUTORS}The information was gathered by Class 4H Kingmoor Junior School: Lucy ARMSTRONG Andrea BALLANTYNE Sarah COCKETT Nina CULLEY Caroline DIGNAN Anneliese FLETCHER Suzanne GOURLAY Emma GROOCOCK Debbie LEATHER Sarah MASON Michelle ROBERTSON & Caroline WYLLIE are the girls. Kevin BAINBRIDGE Andrew GRAHAM Neil HISCOX Matthew HUNT Michael IRWIN Wayne JOHNSTON Paul MARRIOTT Andrew PALMER Craig SLATER Brian WHITWORTH & Anthony WORRALL are the boys. We are one of two top junior classes at the school & we are all 10 or 11 years of age. Our teacher is Mr Hepburn who was a civil engineer before he came into teaching. The photographs were taken by various children in the class.
